FBIS4-1850 "drchi064_r_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-064 Daily Report 2 Apr 1994 North Region Beijing Security Bureau Summons Wei Jingsheng Beijing Security Bureau Summons Wei Jingsheng OW0204131694 Beijing XINHUA in English 1257 GMT 2 Apr 94 OW0204131694 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 2 (XINHUA) -- The Beijing Municipal Public Security Bureau summoned Wei Jingsheng and had a talk with him yesterday. Wei left the bureau immediately afterwards. He was sentenced to 15 years' jail in 1979 for activities endangering state security and was released on parole in September last year with six months of his sentence still to run.
